window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Brick by brick, Arthur and his friends have made Coldbrook into their new home. But can it survive a monster wave? It's going to take everyone and everything for Coldbrook to weather this storm.</b></p> <p>When Arthur first arrived in the Demon World, he couldn't have possibly imagined that one day he would be leading his own town against a horde of monsters. As he works with Coldbrook residents to build up its defenses, he's getting help from unexpected places. Like he was promised, the Demon World is a nice place, and even in the most dire of circumstances, he can still find that promise of nice coming true.</p> <p><i>The fourth volume in a cozy, slice-of-life series.</i></p>"; 
